text: Martin Janco (born 25 January 1995) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for Dubnica as a forward. ==Club career== ===Spartak Myjava=== Janco made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Spartak Myjava on 28 February 2015 against Spartak Trnava.SPARTAK TRNAVA VS.
